I ran into issues with this and suggest that the `__eq__` functions test for type equality
```python
    def __eq__(self, other):
        if not isinstance(other, Unit):
            return False
        return self.tag == other.tag
        
    def __ne__(self, other):
        if not isinstance(other, Unit):
            return True
        return self.tag != other.tag
```

